name: Lanxess Pte Ltd
description: Lanxess is a leading specialty chemicals company with sales of EUR 7.1 billion in 2010. Headquarter in Leverkusen, Germany. id: \nLanxess is growing in Singapore with an investment of EUR 400 million, we will build a butyl rubber plant on Jurong Island.
